QuestData.Title: Lost Lumberjack
QuestData.Description:
All o' them mole machines got mighty unreliable here in Gorgrond. I hear tell that one of 'em might've crashed here in Tangleheart.
See if you can find Frenna. She would've been on the one we tracked to this location. I'll go lookin' for the mole machine to see if it can be repaired.
QuestData.RewardText: Frenna didn't make it out of Tangleheart.
